\subsection{Alternative scale prescriptions}
\label{sec:scale_alternatives}

We test eight scale prescriptions and compute $m_s^{\msbar}(\mu)$ at each, comparing against $\mathcal{F}^2 = 95.1134$~MeV:
\begin{center}
\begin{tabular}{lcc}
\toprule
Prescription & $\mu$ (MeV) & Hit (within $1\sigma$)? \\
\midrule
$\mu_\star = m_e + m_\mu + m_\tau$ (baseline) & $1883.10$ & yes ($+0.06\sigma$) \\
$m_\mu + m_\tau$ & $1882.59$ & yes (trivially equivalent) \\
$m_\tau$ & $1776.93$ & no ($-2.31\sigma$) \\
$2~\text{GeV}$ (conventional reference, not lepton-derived) & $2000.00$ & no ($+2.46\sigma$) \\
